status.Name: Pending
status.Description: This status means that a Order is pending for approval or downpayment or other reason, has not yet begun.

status.Name: Scheduled/Upcoming
status.Description: This status means that a Order has been approved but has not yet begun, is scheduled to be started in the near future but have not yet started.

status.Name: In Progress
status.Description: A Work Order that is currently ongoing and is in progress.

status.Name: Priority
status.Description: The term 'priority' defines how important or urgent a task or work order's goal is in relation to other things.

status.Name: Overdue
status.Description: This indicates that the Work Order has passed its completion date and is behind schedule

status.Name: Canceled
status.Description: The Order ended before completion. This could be due to a variety of factors, including changing goals, budget limits, pending payments or unexpected events
